            <note xml:id="foot.f5"><ref target="../nameregs/nameregs_6668.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">Richard Matthews Ruck</ref> (Amy’s brother), and <ref target="../nameregs/nameregs_1230.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">Leonard Darwin</ref>.</note>
